data.description: This amazing home in Oxford school district features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms with an open floor plan! The bedrooms are laid out in a split bedroom floor plan. The living room boasts a vaulted ceiling. The master bedroom also features a large walk-in closet, private bath, and vaulted ceilings. The other two bedrooms and bathroom are also large. The kitchen features gorgeous granite countertops. The laundry room is large and there are extra linen closets. The back patio is perfect for summertime grilling! Schedule your showing today!
data.whatILove: The neighbors are wonderful.  The  huge back yard has lots of trees with plenty of room to have a pool and a work shop.  Driveway can accommodate at least 2 vehicles.
